  "description": "A close-up photograph showcases a delicate white tulip in full bloom against a stark black background. The petals are slightly ruffled and appear translucent in places, revealing subtle veins and a hint of yellow near the center. The flower's interior features prominent yellow stamens and a green pistil. A single green leaf, blurred due to shallow depth of field, curves gently beside the bloom, adding a touch of natural texture. The lighting is dramatic, highlighting the tulip\u2019s form and creating strong contrasts between light and shadow.",
